h1. Colorized NDVI Datasets

GINA is publishing MODIS NDVI datasets via that have been colorized using a standard pallit via a "Web Mapping Service(WMS)":http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WMS .  This service is intended to provide users a easy and quick way to visualize the NDVI datasets in desktop mapping clients like ArcMap. 

The url for the service is: _"http://ndvi.gina.alaska.edu/modis"_ .

